descmd: This STU Update of the Da Vinci Clinical Data Exchange (CDex) Implementation Guide is the third published version of this guide. The sponsoring [HL7 International/Infrastructure And Messaging Work Group](http://www.hl7.org/Special/committees/inm) members agreed to and voted on the resolution of the community review comments and edits to this guide. For a detailed list of the changes for this version, see the [Change Notes](http://hl7.org/fhir/us/davinci-alerts/STU1.1/changes.html).
